Class Mood

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.projectattitude.projectattitude.Objects.Mood
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Mood
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Created by Chris on 2/24/2017. This is the mood class that represents the heart of this application. The majority of functions here are getters and setters for the various properties of the mood object such as date and trigger.
